Setup Kafka:
Create EC2 instance in AWS 
Download the pem file and in the instance download Java 
Install Java
Start zookeeper
Start Kafka Server 
Create Producer
CreATE consumer

Python:
Connect python to Kafka using kafkaProducer and kafkaConsumer

Push the data to S3 using boto
Use Crawler and push the data into the database
Perform queries using Athena 
